## Create franchise — admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/franchises
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
    "name": "Chainsaw Man",
    "synopsis": "Denji has a simple dream - to live a happy and peaceful life."
}

### Responce
// {"status":"success","code":201,"msg":"Franchise created successfully","data":{"id":10},"timestamp":"2026-03-15 02:19:55"}
### Response (get created franchise)
// {"status":"success","code":200,"msg":"Request success","data":{"id":10,"name":"Chainsaw Man","synopsis":"Denji has a simple dream - to live a happy and peaceful life.","created_at":"2026-03-15 02:19:55","updated_at":"2026-03-15 02:19:55"},"timestamp":"2026-03-15 02:20:21"}


